  <summary date="2022-11-01T16:15:33Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Streamlining EIDL Act

This bill requires the Small Business Administration (SBA) to provide status updates on, review, and approve or disapprove Economic Injury Disaster Loans within certain time frames. It also requires the SBA to report on its efforts to address fraud under the program.</summary>
